{"tid":1802324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【1.1元旦大遊行　不反已出】","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T09:57:17.000Z","uid":173916,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d01d0bb684000981bb85479a77c0d77852521213","tid":1802324,"uid":173916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:30:46.000Z","msg":"民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to<br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n【海報、單張下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QwFg31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QwFg31&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=bbe7274c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QwFg31</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【民陣 TG】 <a href=\"http://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=ad90218f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n【民陣 Twitter】 <a href=\"http://twitter.com/chrf_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchrf_hk&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=fd25c968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/chrf_hk</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣被捕法律支援熱線：6549 9452<br />\nWhatsapp / SMS / Telegram<br />\n<br />\n請提供資料：（＊必要）<br />\n<br />\n1. 被捕地點<br />\n2. 中文全名＊<br />\n3. 英文全名<br />\n4. 身份證號碼<br />\n5. 性別、年齡<br />\n6. 當事人電話<br />\n7. 所在警署<br />\n8. 緊急聯絡人電話＊<br />\n9. 報料人電話＊（若與緊急聯絡人不同）<br />\n10. 其他詳情（如有）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTTFVrq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2